Project Overview:-

This repository contains simple Python programs designed to practice basic logic building and problem-solving.
These are beginner-friendly tasks useful for interviews and coding fundamentals.

Files Included

1️.Time Converter
Description:
Converts minutes into hours and remaining minutes.

Example:
Input: 130
Output: 2 hrs 10 minutes

Concepts Used:
Integer division (//)
Modulus operator (%)
User input handling

2️.Remove Duplicates from String
Description:
Removes duplicate characters from a string while preserving order.

Example:
Input: programming
Output: progamin

Concepts Used:
Loops (for)
String manipulation
Conditional logic

3.Technologies Used
Python 
Basic Input/Output
Core Programming Concepts

4.How to Run
Install Python
Clone this repository
Run any file using:
python filename.py

5.Learning Outcomes
Strong understanding of basic logic
Practice with loops and conditions
Writing clean and simple Python code
Problem-solving skills improvement


If you found this helpful, give it a ⭐ on GitHub!
